Class SewolOnt.Case

  • java.lang.Object
    • odase.Individual
      • odase.wf.sewol.SewolOnt.Case
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    SewolOnt

    public static class SewolOnt.Case
extends Individual
implements Serializable
    A workflow defines a context in which tasks can be executed. It defines the conditions where a set of tasks can exists.
